S.FORM: Frank Brickowski nalecuhan i Bayville, New York, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Frank Brickowski i 1981 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 3 ku uwac atu silsil 57, namapili' tu nu New York Knicks putiput. tatama, nalecuhan i 8 a bulad 14 a demiad, 1959 a mihcan, Frank Brickowski, u miunduay ciniza. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
